msContents.summary: Manual of Greek Orthodox canon law. Includes a fragmentary index or table of contents on the first 13 f. (numbered p. 4-5, 8-29, [30-31]); two leaves are missing).

msItem.title: Manual of Greek Orthodox Canon Law
msItem.author: Orthodox Eastern Church

supportDesc.extent: 204 leaves : 207 x 153 (141 x 105) mm. bound to 215 x 164 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, i + 202 + i; [i], 5, 8-29, [ii], 1-373, [vii]; contemporary or near-contemporary pagination in ink; [1-404], modern pagination in pencil, upper outer corners.

binding.p: Contemporary parchment. Cover shows traces of a text; the cover may be a palimpsest, or else the text may have been transferred from another manuscript which was pressed up against the cover and got wet. Much staining, probably from water. Some oxidation of ink. Several worm holes. Some leaves torn. First extant folio badly stained and damaged; some text partly obliterated. Cover slightly warped.
